# `npx skills add` side-effects. We vendor the official HyperFrames skill
# under skills/hyperframes/ (with an OD frontmatter shim) instead of relying
# on per-agent skill loaders, so the lockfile + auto-installed agent dirs
# above are derivative and never need to be committed. To refresh from
# upstream, run `node scripts/sync-hyperframes-skill.mjs`.
skills-lock.json

# Commander task scratchpad; keep local task notes out of git by default.
.task/
